name: Pluto
description:
TLDR My gf told me, that I would never sell photo of our dog as NFT. Prove her wrong.

Meet Sir Pluto!
Greatest golden retriever in this timeline.
He's one and a half ears old, he is full of life and energy. He loves his toys and his mom (my girlfriend, more on that later) and dad (thats me :D). 
Also is saving my life from panic attacks and anxiety. 

Few days ago, I tried to describe all this NFT stuff to my girlfriend, and she kinda "got it, 
but not too much"!
And she also told me, that I would never sell picture of our dog as NFT.
So, prove her wrong! :D
